About the game: Sensei challenge you! This is a hardcore arcade game in which you will need to complete level in less than 5 seconds! 5.0 - infinite arcade game focusing on making the high score. You will play as a young ninja who needs to get to his sensei avoiding all obstacles on his way. 5 seconds to complete the level, or die trying! Levels will change randomly and so do the locations of your sensei. It`s a real challenge even for hardcore gamers. Do you think you can master it? Then show to yourself and your sensei who is a real ninja here! Features: - 40 unique levels - simple control - dynamic gameplay - cool pixel art - oldschool style - achievements - no text, only pure action. Serious.
